  "detailed_description": "You can try the restaurant simulation with your friends online or locally.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1820380/extras/2098756e70769a4c83e67437fc0f5fba.avif?t=1730489001\" width=500 height=292 /></span><br><br>You can enter with a maximum of 16 people.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1820380/extras/97f921d8e5ed483f9c7389a2372c10b3.avif?t=1730489001\" width=500 height=292 /></span><br><br>You can play alone if you want (it will be difficult.).<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1820380/extras/c4a8128f795080fe2d4c3e8f6fc3dff1.avif?t=1730489001\" width=500 height=292 /></span><br><br>You will enter with your friends and manage the restaurant by working as both a waiter and a cook.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1820380/extras/4319f0c738664445b1ab5815041f1d5c.avif?t=1730489001\" width=500 height=292 /></span><br><br>You will buy the necessary materials in the kitchen from the market with in-game money (not real money) and quickly prepare the incoming orders in the kitchen and manage the restaurant.",
  "about_the_game": "You can try the restaurant simulation with your friends online or locally.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1820380/extras/2098756e70769a4c83e67437fc0f5fba.avif?t=1730489001\" width=500 height=292 /></span><br><br>You can enter with a maximum of 16 people.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1820380/extras/97f921d8e5ed483f9c7389a2372c10b3.avif?t=1730489001\" width=500 height=292 /></span><br><br>You can play alone if you want (it will be difficult.).<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1820380/extras/c4a8128f795080fe2d4c3e8f6fc3dff1.avif?t=1730489001\" width=500 height=292 /></span><br><br>You will enter with your friends and manage the restaurant by working as both a waiter and a cook.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1820380/extras/4319f0c738664445b1ab5815041f1d5c.avif?t=1730489001\" width=500 height=292 /></span><br><br>You will buy the necessary materials in the kitchen from the market with in-game money (not real money) and quickly prepare the incoming orders in the kitchen and manage the restaurant.",
